    "ideation": "This emoji represents a delicate mix of ambivalence, mild skepticism, and uneasy 'meh'. The core of the performance is the misalignment between the eyes and the mouth. I start with a neutral, slightly confused face, then shift the gaze to a point of slight concern while introducing the diagonal mouth. The diagonal mouth is achieved by setting the frequency very low and using phase to create a non-zero baseline slope. The asymmetry in the eyes (one slightly more open/raised than the other) creates that 'I'm not quite sure how I feel about this' energy. The colors are muted, dusty, and uncertain—a blend of pale ochre and greyish-olive.",
